				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">Bregalad wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Why use 20 IRQs when you could just play a longer sample with adjusted lenght/duration ratio, and use only 1 on them ?</div>
<br />Because we have to measure how long it takes for the first IRQ to fire (so that this difference is used to compensate the timing later), and if you use a larger interval you'll waste a lot of time waiting for this IRQ to happen.
<br />
<br />EDIT: <a href="http://membler-industries.com/tokumaru/dmc_20100826.zip" class="postlink">Here's all the work I've done on this</a>. Don't expect any documentation or clean code though. Feel free to do whatever you want with this.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

